channel.title: Log in error
channel.description:
My friend made this server a while ago, and it just updated yesterday, and it moved server, but when we moved server, we can't log in.
Well, we can, but when you do it goes to the page when your logged in with all the rules, you know? and then it always looses connection and "tries to reestablish" but fails, and your logged out, then when you try to log back in, it says your account is already logged in, so i made multiple accounts and it happend each time, also for other people. Can you guys test it/tell me whats wrong?
Port 5555 rksscape.no-ip.org
Thanks..... Th3 G0d Scape administrator, Tramposch
(im getting a picture)
We added a bunch of new commands, like clans.. pk box.... things like that..
